25 registration, by appearing in person during the period for early voting or on election day. To
26 register to vote during such periods, an elector must provide his or her driver’s license or
27 identification card issued by the Department of Motor Vehicles and, if the license or
28 identification card does not include his or her current residential address, certain documents
29 establishing proof of residency. (NRS 293.5837-293.5847)
